        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 540,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6250,
            "LocalizeKR": "마, 맞아!\n한눈에 알아보다니!\n역시 스승님!",
            "LocalizeJP": "そ、そう！\n一目で気がつくなんて！\nさすが師匠！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 550,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9250,
            "LocalizeKR": "스, 스승님을 위해서,\n준비한 거야…!",
            "LocalizeJP": "し、師匠のために、\n用意してきたものなんだ……！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 560,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8800,
            "LocalizeKR": "지금까지 선생님에겐\n억지를 부리기만 했지,\n제대로 된 답례는,\n하지도 못했고……",
            "LocalizeJP": "これまで先生には、\nワガママを言ってばかりで、\nちゃんとしたお礼は、\nできてなかったし……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 570,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11700,
            "LocalizeKR": "폐를 끼쳤으니까…\n그, 감사의\n마음이라고 할까……",
            "LocalizeJP": "迷惑をかけちゃったから……\nその、感謝の\n気持ちというか……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 580,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3400,
            "LocalizeKR": "처, 처음 만들어본 거니까… ",
            "LocalizeJP": "は、初めて作ったから……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 590,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4900,
            "LocalizeKR": "그다지, 맛은\n보증할 수 없을지도……",
            "LocalizeJP": "あんまり、味は保証\nできない、かも……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 600,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5100,
            "LocalizeKR": "이런 거, 나에겐\n조금 이르지 않나,\n싶기도 하지만…",
            "LocalizeJP": "こういうの、アタシには\nちょっと早い気も、\nするけど……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10082,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1008201,
            "DisplayOrder": 610,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9100,
            "LocalizeKR": "그, 그래도,\n열심히 했으니까…!",
            "LocalizeJP": "で、でも、\n頑張ったんだ……！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
